snippet.textDisplay: You can tell by your statement “Natural Hair is soooo dry” that you probably don’t service a lot of natural curly clients. Natural hair isn’t automatically dry. When you lack moisture (water) then your hair will feel dry due to you not properly taking care of your hair etc. There are a lot of people who have naturally curly hair who isn’t dry, so that statement is wrong and extremely misleading. 🙄🤨
